   Presentations
   [dot_clea.gif]
   Purchase PowerPoint All files available for download on this page are
   stored in the either PowerPoint or QuickTime Format. Microsoft
   PowerPoint must be used to view the PowerPoint presentation files; and
   Apple QuickTime must be used to view the QuickTime movie files.

   If you do not have Microsoft PowerPoint, you may purchase it by
   clicking on the logo, above right. If you do not have Apple Quicktime,
   you may download a free copy by clicking on the Get QuickTime logo,
   below right.

   These presentations may be freely reused without copywrite
   restrictions.

   IMPORTANT: For PowerPoint presentations that contain QuickTime movies
   (presentation titles noted with an asterisk), one MUST download the
   QuickTime movies individually (links are provided, below). Depending on
   one's platform and PowerPoint version, you may need to re-link the
   QuickTime movies to the PowerPoint presentation. If you have any
   problems with this, contact Paul Hubanks at
   hubanks@climate.gsfc.nasa.gov.
